## 🚀 Before You Deploy to Vercel

| # | Action | Status |
|---|--------|--------|
| 1 | Set `VITE_ACCESS_CODE` in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables | ⬜ Pending |
| 2 | Set `VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY` in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables | ⬜ Pending |
| 3 | Push changes to Git (confirm no `.env` files are committed) | ⬜ Pending |
| 4 | Verify `dist/` is NOT committed (`git status` should not show it) | ⬜ Pending |
| 5 | Deploy on Vercel and test `/api/analyze` endpoint | ⬜ Pending |
| 6 | Open browser DevTools → Network tab → verify API key is invisible | ⬜ Pending |
| 7 | Test access gate with wrong codes (should lock out after 5 attempts) | ⬜ Pending |
| 8 | Verify no compliance badges appear in the UI | ⬜ Pending |

